When these paths or patterns are touched, consult `database-agent` before finalization. See also [.cursor/docs/orchestration-routing.md](.cursor/docs/orchestration-routing.md) for the full matrix.

Required for L2+:
- database review summary present in task closeout
- verification notes include database-sensitive checks where relevant

Do not finalize schema/migration-sensitive work without database specialist evidence.
